Help Ahmad and his family

Florence King is organizing this fundraiser.
Donation protected
I'm Florence from the UK, I set up this fundraiser for Ahmad Al-Mashharawy.

Hello, my name is Ahmed. I live with my family in Gaza, consisting of 6 people.

Since the war began on us, our lives have changed for the unknown and the worst. We have been displaced from the north to the south to a place resembling a desert, searching for security and safety. Our home was destroyed. All the fatigue of the years evaporated in the blink of an eye.

My family and I live in a small tent that is not even fit for animals. Since the beginning of the war, we have lost everything. Our lives, dreams and future have been destroyed. There is no safe place. We stand on our feet to move from one place to another to save ourselves from the bombing and destruction. Searching for water and scarce food that we acquire with difficulty and fatigue for fear of dying of hunger, thirst or disease, not to mention the amount of epidemics and deadly and contagious diseases for which there are no medicines due to the closure of the crossings on us from all directions.

We have lost contact with my brother and now we do not know if he is alive or missing and without a fate or trace? Our lives have become hell.

Life is getting worse and more difficult every day.

There is no source of income for me and my family and no one has helped us since the tyrannical war began.

Help us to live in security and peace. My family and I are living a life that the human mind cannot comprehend and even iron cannot bear.

Help us to achieve our dreams and shine with a bright future.

Now I and others do not study or work. I have become just a number. I have no goal in life because of the devastating war that has exhausted us.

Please donate even a little so that my family and I can evacuate and travel outside the country and receive treatment to any place in search of safety.

Thank you
